<DOCNO> LA022690-0011 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 181563 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
February 26, 1990, Monday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 7; Column 3; Op-Ed Desk 
</P>
