<P>
BLACKS -- CULTURE; TEENAGE PREGNANCY; INDIGENTS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA022690-0042 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 181672 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
February 26, 1990, Monday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
