<P>
Disney Sues Fox Over Programming: The Buena Vista Television unit of Walt 
Disney Co. filed an antitrust suit Wednesday in U.S. District Court against Fox 
Broadcasting Inc. and several affiliate companies. 
</P>
<P>
The suit alleges that Fox is trying to prevent stations from carrying "The 
Disney Afternoon," a two-hour children's program still in development. Fox had 
no comment on the suit. (Filed Feb. 21; Case No. CV90-0875RG) 
