<HEADLINE>
<P>
MARKET WATCH; 
</P>
<P>
WEEKLY SCORECARD; 
</P>
<P>
MUTUAL FUNDS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Average total return, including dividends, in percent for periods ended 
