TRUMP QUESTIONS ALL THE FUSS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Times Staff and Wire Service Reports 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
NEW YORK 
</P>
