<TEXT>
<P>
Donald Trump seems surprised that his split with his wife, Ivana, has been such 
a running story in the New York tabloids and the British press. In a 
rush-to-print interview in the upcoming New York magazine, the billionaire 
developer expressed surprise that coverage of the Steven Spielberg-Amy Irving 
and Jane Fonda-Tom Hayden splits were such one-day stories, while his goes on 
and on. 
</P>
